## ── Secrets & Konfigurasi Sensitif ─────────────────────────────────────────
# JANGAN commit file ini — berisi JWT key, connection string, dll.
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
appsettings.Production.json
secrets.json

# .NET User Secrets (disimpan lokal per developer)
# Path: ~/.microsoft/usersecrets/<guid>/secrets.json
# File referensinya ada di .csproj (UserSecretsId), bukan di sini

